946c2cf030e6dfed30e4346a5302589c  docker-man-1.0.0.tar.gz"
sha256sums="ae10d8262e531bb4b6cff37fd3ec491ba5a5273f472607df592918f796004865  docker-1.0.0.tar.gz
d47f5e7b950818c0a50ef6defb59fa52a709b77dee94679709fe601d1fc6f5cc  docker-man-1.0.0.tar.gz"
sha512sums="3bdd556c41995644dcb667c075ca6cac06134089ea8085f1494f38588100f19c25e5d7a6fc752f38f58c63d0a49a77dec941a9dfe77af937727e5fae6eb43861  docker-1.0.0.tar.gz
